{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fee3044e7d","title":"对军事建设五年计划的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cc343e27fa","index":0,"year":1952,"month":7,"day":18,"articleId":"fee3044e7d"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"f04c4b7a53","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fee3044e7d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。朱，指朱德。周，指周恩来。陈，指陈云，当时任中共中央书记处书记、政务院副总理兼财政经济委员会主任。彭，指彭德怀，当时任人民革命军事委员会副主席。慧，指慧荣臻，当时任中国人民解放军代总参谋长。票，指票裕，当时任中国人民解放军副总参谋长。"},{"id":"2578e11676","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fee3044e7d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林，指林彪，当时任人民革命军事委员会副主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"27db0b1ca5","type":"title","text":"对军事建设五年计划的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fee3044e7d"},{"id":"f04c4b7a53","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、朱、周、陈、彭、慧、菜同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fee3044e7d"},{"id":"2578e11676","type":"paragraph","text":"慧、菜所拟军事五年计划及附件已阅过，基本同意，可即照此部署，请彭主持。此件抄本周处已有，现将我的一份送刘、朱、陈、林四同志阅，阅后退毛。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fee3044e7d"},{"id":"7cfb3a2c62","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fee3044e7d"},{"id":"02d886b315","type":"paragraph","text":"七月十八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fee3044e7d"}],"page":{"id":"154d53c789","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fee3044e7d","start":172,"end":172}}}},"__N_SSG":true}